        <p>The Imperial College Investment Club (ICIC) was formerly a subsidiary of the Imperial College Finance Society (ICFS), specialising in the trading and investing side of the financial world. The club had a rich history, with its many initiatives and opportunities helping its members find that dream job in trading or asset management year after year. The club had two main aims:</p>
