        <p>Educating members with the theory and providing them with a platform to apply that theory and gain practical experience was at the heart of the ICIC's ethos. However due to external restrictions on its trading activities, the ICIC had to cease many of its initiatives last year. In order to preserve the highly beneficial aspects of the ICIC that provided enormous value to members over the years, the ICIC merged with the ICFS. As a result, this year the benefits of the ICIC will continue to act as the springboard for future financial careers by opening themselves up to even more members than ever before. </p>
